<body>
    <header class="site-header" id="header">
        <a href="https://koshank.com/"><img src="https://koshank.com/assets/images/koshank.png" alt="koshank logo" style="width:10%; background-color: black; border-radius: 50%;"></a>
        <h1  data-lead-id="site-header-title" style="font-size: 50px; font-weight: 600%;">Cancellation And Refund</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="main-content">
        <h2 style="text-align: left;">Cancellation Policy</h2>
        <p class="main-content__body" data-lead-id="main-content-body" style="text-align: left;">1.1 <strong>Course Enrollment:</strong> When you enroll in our online digital marketing courses, you are making a commitment to participate and benefit from the learning experience. You may request to cancel your enrollment, but please note the following conditions: <br> 1.2 <strong>Refund Period:</strong> We offer a 7 days refund period from the date of enrollment. If you wish to cancel within this period, you are eligible for a full refund, no questions asked. <br> 1.3 <strong>Refund Request:</strong> To initiate a refund, please contact our customer support team at koshank.com@gmail.com. We may require additional information to process your request. <br> 1.4 <strong>No Refund After Refund Period:</strong> After the refund period expires, we do not provide refunds for course enrollments. <br> 1.5 <strong>Time To Refund:</strong> Payment Will Take Atleast 10-15 Working Days To Get Credited In Customers Account Once The Refund Is Initiated From Koshank Team.</p>
        <h2 style="text-align: left;">Refund Policy</h2>
        <p class="main-content__body" data-lead-id="main-content-body" style="text-align: left;">2.1 <strong>Course Content:</strong> We strive to provide high-quality digital marketing courses that deliver value. However, if you are dissatisfied with the course content or experience, please contact us to discuss your concerns. We are committed to addressing your feedback and making improvements where necessary. <br> 2.2 <strong>Refund Eligibility:</strong> Refunds are considered on a case-by-case basis for circumstances such as technical issues preventing course access or dissatisfaction with course content. Refund eligibility will be determined at our discretion. <br> 2.3 <strong>Refund Process:</strong> To request a refund, please contact our customer support team at [Insert Contact Information]. Provide specific details regarding your situation, including your course enrollment information. We will review your request and respond promptly. <br> 2.4 <strong>No Refunds for Completed Courses:</strong> We do not provide refunds for courses that have been completed or partially completed.</p>
        <h2 style="text-align: left;">Additional Information</h2>
        <p class="main-content__body" data-lead-id="main-content-body" style="text-align: left;">3.1 <strong>Processing Time:</strong> Refund processing times may vary depending on your payment method and financial institution. We will make every effort to process your refund as quickly as possible. <br> 3.2 <strong>Course Access:</strong> Upon cancellation and refund approval, your access to the course content will be revoked.</p>
        <h2 style="text-align: left;">Changes To Policy</h2>
        <p class="main-content__body" data-lead-id="main-content-body" style="text-align: left;">4.1 We reserve the right to update or modify this Cancellation and Refund Policy at any time without prior notice. Any changes will be reflected on this page</p>
        <h2 style="text-align: left;">Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="main-content__body" data-lead-id="main-content-body" style="text-align: left;">If you have any questions, concerns, or requests related to this Cancellation And Refund Policy, please contact us at:<br><br>Koshank<br>Email: koshank.com@gmail.com <br><br>Thank you for trusting us with your personal information. We are committed to maintaining your privacy and providing you with quality digital marketing courses.</p>
